title: Part Three:  An NBA Skins Draft Plus Award Predictions | With Ryen Russillo and Joe House
description:
In Part 3 of a three-part podcast, The Ringer’s Bill Simmons is joined by Ryen Russillo and Joe House to draft NBA teams’ wins and losses in a skins style game (1:24). Then they make their predictions for NBA awards for the 2022-23 season (15:53).

Host: Bill Simmons
Guests: Ryen Russillo and Joe House
Producer: Kyle Crichton
